Zapret2 DPI Bypass Plugin for OPNsense

Provides a GUI-managed anti-censorship tool using zapret2 (https://github.com/bol-van/zapret2).
Bypasses deep packet inspection (DPI) used by ISPs to block websites via SNI filtering.

Features:
- dvtws2 divert socket integration (ipfw)
- Configurable DPI desynchronization strategies
- Domain hostlist support
- Blockcheck diagnostics
- Automatic ipfw/ipdivert kernel module management

WWW: https://github.com/ugorur/os-zapret2
